Alvarion Rises Most in Four Weeks on $2 Million Angola Contract

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-10-05T10:16:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/alvarion-rises-most-in-four-weeks-on-2-million-angola-contract.html
Alvarion Ltd. (ALVR)  advanced the most in
almost four weeks after saying it won a $2 million contract with
Angola Communications Systems to install a high-speed wireless
broadband network in the African nation.  The shares gained 2.9 percent, the biggest intraday gain
since Sept. 8, to 3.92 shekels at 12:02 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Tel Aviv at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  